66
00:10:34,775 --> 00:10:36,397
Are you sure you can handle it?

67
00:10:38,917 --> 00:10:39,917
Yeah.

68
00:11:57,712 --> 00:12:01,498
Aunt Noi told me that
before Sophida was bitten,

69
