81
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:45,485
You lead the way. I'll watch your back.

82
00:12:45,485 --> 00:12:46,485
Let's go.

83
00:12:47,809 --> 00:12:48,809
Come on.

84
00:12:53,335 --> 00:12:57,209
