Prach, we have to help Beam.

85
00:12:57,893 --> 00:12:58,893
Put it down.

86
00:12:59,592 --> 00:13:00,596
That's right.

87
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:04,020
Dr. Beam is the main one we're looking for.

88
00:13:05,003 --> 00:13:10,702
Dr. Beam, it's just me, you, and Run
